The '''slender-billed starling''' ('''''Onychognathus tenuirostris''''') is a species of [[starling]] in the family [[Sturnidae]]. It is found in [[Burundi]], [[Democratic Republic of the Congo]], [[Eritrea]], [[Ethiopia]], [[Kenya]], [[Malawi]], [[Rwanda]], [[Tanzania]], [[Uganda]], and [[Zambia]].<ref name="iucn status 17 November 2021" />

